                      <br>
                      <b>RECRUITMENT QUEST<br>
                      <br></b><br>
                      <br>
                      <b>[120] Crusader of Light: For Their Rest</b><br>
                      Prerequisites: Completed<a href="/page/Armonia+Episode+1" target="_self">Armonia Episode 1</a>scenario.<br>
                      <ol>
                        <li>Talk to Sirius in Armonia Cathedral (F3).</li>
                        <li>Talk to Saint Anis in Armonia Cathedral (F3/G3).</li>
                        <li>Trigger a combat mission (<i>&quot;Warrior&#39;s Earrings&quot;</i>, 30 minutes) in Armonia En Celar (G7).
                          <ul>
                            <li>Kill all the corrupted monsters in the mission.</li>
                            <li>When the last corrupted monster is dead, you will acquire Warrior&#39;s Earrings (quest item).</li>
                            <li>Tip: There is no need for Holy Water of Armonia in this mission.</li>
                          </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Talk to Sirius in Armonia Cathedral (F3) to give him the above quest item.</li>
                        <li>Collect Warrior&#39;s Earrings (quest item) x20 by killing Corrupted Guards in Armonia En Celar.</li>
                        <li>Talk to Sirius in Armonia Cathedral (F3).</li>
                      </ol>
                      <blockquote>
                        <b><i>Corrupted Lanceman</i></b> &bull; Lv.130 Demon &bull; Light Armor &bull; None &bull; Medium<br>
                        HP 2,260,440 &bull; ATK Rating 67 &bull; ATK 33,750 &bull; DEF Rating 65 &bull; DEF 187<br>
                        Penetration 0 &bull; Magic Penetration - Fire 0, Ice 0, Lightning 0, Mental 0<br>
                        Immunity 0 &bull; RES - Fire 25, Ice 25, Lightning 25, Mental 70<br>
                        <br>
                        <b><i>Corrupted Guard</i></b> &bull; Lv.130 Demon &bull; Soft Armor &bull; None &bull; Small<br>
                        HP 2,260,440 &bull; ATK Rating 68 &bull; ATK 33,750 &bull; DEF Rating 65 &bull; DEF 187<br>
                        Penetration 10 &bull; Magic Penetration - Fire 0, Ice 0, Lightning 0, Mental 0<br>
                        Immunity 0 &bull; RES - Fire 70, Ice 25, Lightning 25, Mental 25<br>
                        <br>
                        <b><i>Corrupted Peltast</i></b> &bull; Lv.130 Demon &bull; Heavy Armor &bull; None &bull; Small<br>
                        HP 2,260,440 &bull; ATK Rating 65 &bull; ATK 33,750 &bull; DEF Rating 68 &bull; DEF 187<br>
                        Penetration 0 &bull; Magic Penetration - Fire 0, Ice 0, Lightning 0, Mental 0<br>
                        Immunity 30 &bull; RES - Fire 25, Ice 70, Lightning 25, Mental 25
                      </blockquote><br>
                      <b>[120] Crusader of Light: Memorial Ceremony of Armonia</b><br>
                      Prerequisites: Completed the quests above.<br>
                      <ol>
                        <li>Talk to Saint Anis in Armonia Cathedral (F3/G3).</li>
                        <li>Collect Ruddy Armonium (quest item) x1 by killing Abyss Bear in Armonia Latina.
                          <ul>
                            <li>Abyss Bear spawns at E7. Abyss Bear spawns 1-2 hours after Abyss Wolf died, and vice versa.</li>
                            <li>Abyss Bear has a huge area attack, but if the squad can kill it fast, it won&#39;t be an issue.</li>
                            <li>When killed, it drops a few Elohim Boxes (aka Armonia Reward Boxes), and there will be a zone-wide notice that Abyss Bear/Wolf has been killed by [player&#39;s name] family.</li>
                            <li>Squad everyone to get the kill. Don&#39;t be selfish and kill it out of squad, depriving others of the quest item. Helping others won&#39;t deprive you of it.</li>
                          </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Talk to Saint Anis in Armonia Cathedral (F3/G3) to give her the above quest item and to receive Holy Water of Armonia for the Memorial Ceremony (quest item).</li>
                        <li>Talk to Sirius in Armonia Cathedral (F3) to give him the above quest item.</li>
                      </ol>
                      <blockquote>
                        <b><i>Abyss Bear</i></b> &bull; Lv.140 Wildlife &bull; Heavy Armor &bull; None &bull; Large<br>
                        HP 2,808,000 &bull; ATK Rating 72 &bull; ATK 177,408 &bull; DEF Rating 77 &bull; DEF 240<br>
                        Penetration 0 &bull; Magic Penetration - Fire 0, Ice 0, Lightning 0, Mental 0<br>
                        Immunity 60 &bull; RES - Fire 33, Ice 33, Lightning 33, Mental 31
                      </blockquote>
                      <div align="center"></div><br>
                      <b>[120] Crusader of Light: Rest In Peace In Heaven</b><br>
                      Prerequisites: Completed the quests above.<br>
                      <ol>
                        <li>Trigger a non-combat mission (<i>&quot;Pledge Carved In The Earring&quot;</i>) in Armonia Cathedral (F3).</li>
                        <li>Talk to Sirius in Armonia Cathedral (F3).</li>
                      </ol><br>
                      <b>[120] Crusader of Light: Preparation For Dispatch</b><br>
                      Prerequisites: Completed the quests above.<br>
                      <ol>
                        <li>Talk to Sirius in Armonia Cathedral (F3) to receive Alliance Document (quest item).</li>
                        <li>Talk to Millionaire Andres in Cite de Armonia (E9) to give him the above quest item.</li>
                        <li>Talk to Millionaire Andres in Cite de Armonia (E9). He will ask for 5 sets of items.
                          <ul>
                            <li>Brawn x30 + Spider Meat x30 + Comodo Meat x30</li>
                            <li>Cabosse x30 + Beet x30 + Golden Apple x30</li>
                            <li>Honey x50 + Wheat Flour x50 + Cook Stone x50</li>
                            <li>Pure Etretanium x500 + Pure Aidanium x500 + Pure Quartz x500 + Pure Ionium x500 + Pure Talt x500</li>
                            <li>Mega Etretanium x50 + Mega Aidanium x50 + Mega Quartz x50 + Mega Ionium x50 + Mega Talt x50</li>
                          </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Talk to Millionaire Andres in Cite de Armonia (E9) repeatedly to give him all the items above and receive Credit Letter of Andres (quest item).</li>
                        <li>Talk to Sirius in Armonia Cathedral (F3).</li>
                      </ol><br>
                      <b>[120] The Crusader Sirius Rigel</b><br>
                      Prerequisites: Completed the quests above.<br>
                      Reward: Sirius Character Card, White Gold Bar x5, Training Card G x10, Expert G EXP Card x20.<br>
                      <ol>
                        <li>Talk to Archbishop Lenon in Armonia Cathedral (I4).</li>
                        <li>Talk to Archbishop Vega in Armonia Cathedral (D4).</li>
                        <li>Talk to Sirius in Armonia Cathedral (F3).</li>
                        <li>Talk to Commander William in Armonia Apostadero (H8).</li>
                        <li>Talk to Sirius in Armonia Cathedral (F3) for reward.</li>
                      </ol><br>
                      <br>
                      <b>[120] Sacred Shield: Qualification of the Crusaders</b><br>
                      Prerequisites: Completed <i>Recruit Sirius</i> quests (see above).<br>
                      Reward: [Holy Shielder] Stance Book, Expert G EXP Card x10, Training Card G x5.<br>
                      <ol>
                        <li>Talk to Sirius in Armonia Cathedral (F3).</li>
